<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Arcade de Preguntas - Challenge Hub</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #2b2d42 0%, #1b1d2a 45%, #0f1119 100%);
            color: #ececec;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 2px, transparent 2px),
                              radial-gradient(circle at 80% 40%, rgba(255,255,255,0.06) 2px, transparent 2px);
            background-size: 120px 120px;
        }

        h1, h2, .btn-submit, .btn-add {
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c5ce7 0%, #a29bfe 40%, #ffd368 100%);
            color: #1b1d2a;
            padding: 40px 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255,255,255,0.15), transparent 22%),
                              radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(255,255,255,0.1), transparent 25%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.1rem;
            color: #1b1d2a;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
        }

        header p {
            margin: 12px auto 24px;
            max-width: 700px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #2d2b48;
        }

        .main-nav {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            z-index: 1;
            position: relative;
        }

        .main-nav a {
            color: #1b1d2a;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 18px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(27,29,42,0.2);
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
        }

        .main-nav a:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
        }

        .user-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 16px;
            padding: 12px 18px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            color: #1b1d2a;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            border: 2px dashed rgba(27,29,42,0.18);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .container {
            width: min(95%, 1040px);
            margin: -40px auto 50px;
            background: rgba(16, 18, 34, 0.95);
            padding: 32px;
            border-radius: 28px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        }

        .panel {
            padding: 22px;
            border-radius: 22px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        th, td {
            padding: 16px 18px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
        }

        th {
            color: #f8f9ff;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        tr:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        }

        .actions a {
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .actions a:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .edit {
            background: #7b5cff;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .delete {
            background: #ff6b6b;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #cfd8ff;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }

        .form-group input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            color: #f8f9ff;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            outline: none;
        }

        .form-group input:focus {
            border-color: #7b5cff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(123,92,255,0.12);
        }

        .btn-submit {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 16px 18px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7b5cff, #6c5ce7);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 18px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn-submit:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 18px 30px rgba(123,92,255,0.24);
        }

        .btn-add {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #6c5ce7;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-add:hover {
            background-color: #a29bfe;
            color: #1b1d2a;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #c9d6ff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .back-link:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Arcade Challenge</h1>
    <p>Bienvenido al centro de respuesta más divertido. Regístrate, valida tu correo y supera los retos.</p>
    <nav class="main-nav">
        <a href="/tpfinal_mvc/game/home">Inicio</a>
        {{^loggedIn}}
        <a href="/tpfinal_mvc/game/registro">Registro</a>
        <a href="/tpfinal_mvc/game/login">Login</a>
        {{/loggedIn}}
        {{#loggedIn}}
        <a href="/tpfinal_mvc/game/perfil">Mi perfil</a>
        <a href="/tpfinal_mvc/game/quiz?q=0">Desafíos</a>
        <a href="/tpfinal_mvc/game/logout">Salir</a>
        {{/loggedIn}}
    </nav>

    {{#loggedIn}}
    <div class="user-badge">
        Hola, {{username}}. {{^validated}}Tu correo aún no está validado.{{/validated}}{{#validated}}Tu correo está validado.{{/validated}}
    </div>
    {{/loggedIn}}
</header>
